// CSI Pm h  Set Mode (SM).
//     Ps = 2  -> Keyboard Action Mode (AM).
//     Ps = 4  -> Insert Mode (IRM).
//     Ps = 1 2  -> Send/receive (SRM).
//     Ps = 2 0  -> Automatic Newline (LNM).
// CSI ? Pm h
